_mode - BUTTON_NORMAL creates a generic button BUTTON_LOAD creates a button which opens a file dialog use getFilePath() to retrieve the path to the file
img - sprite source image, sprites must be square loading a sprite (vertical) |------|------|------| |-[0]U-|-[1]O-|-[2]D-| |------|------|------| up, over, down
